snippet.textDisplay: After seeing the 6 minute prologue before an IMAX screening of Star Wars, it seems like they are using a device to manipulate time. Either slowing it down, hurrying it up or turning it back. Washington's character seems like the only one who is able to use this function as he's the only one reacting to the time manipulation scenes in the trailer. I'm sure once the final trailer comes out, we'll have a bit more of an idea but I'm glad that it's got people thinking. Can't wait for July 2020.

The movie ( in my opinion) will try to explain that we must see some things with another angle in order to comprehend it.
